    <title>Hexo about页面及toc相关设置</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2019/10/16/Hexo-about%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2019/10/16/Hexo-about页面相关设置/</id>
    <published>2019-10-16T02:14:21.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-10-16T03:51:57.014Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="about页面新建及设置"><a href="#about页面新建及设置" class="headerlink" title="about页面新建及设置"></a>about页面新建及设置</h1><p>首先新建about页面，进入博客根目录下，在Terminal中输入如下：</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new<span class="built_in"> page </span><span class="string">"about"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>创建完成后可用在<code>source/about/</code>目录下看到一个<strong>index.md</strong>文件<br>接着进入Hexo配置文件<code>博客根目录/themes/hexo-themes-next/_config.yml</code>中<br>找到<code>menu</code>,将<code>about</code>前面注释去掉</p><h1 id="about页面禁用自动toc生成"><a href="#about页面禁用自动toc生成" class="headerlink" title="about页面禁用自动toc生成"></a>about页面禁用自动toc生成</h1><p>about页面在编写过程中出现左侧文章目录看着很不舒服，禁用方法如下：<br>首先在主题下的_config.yml文件中找到toc所在配置，代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Table Of Contents in the Sidebar</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">toc:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Automatically add list number to toc.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  number:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># If true, all words will placed on next lines if header width longer then sidebar width.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  wrap:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>分析这段代码可以得知，toc相关配置在Sidebar文件中，该文件路径为：<code>主题根目录/layout/_macro/sidebar.swig</code><br>目录生成自动，同时自动对多级目录进行编号且超过长度的标题不换行显示完整<br>分析生成的博客<strong>Html</strong>源码，我们可以发现，目录所在位置如下：<br><img src="/images/sidebar_toc.png" alt="sidebar_toc"><br>在<code>sidebar.swig</code>文件中，找到如下代码：</p><figure class="highlight twig"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="xml"></span><span class="template-tag">&#123;% <span class="name"><span class="keyword">set</span></span> display_toc = is_post and theme.toc.enable or is_page and theme.toc.enable %&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"></span><span class="template-tag">&#123;% <span class="name"><span class="keyword">if</span></span> display_toc and toc(page.content).length &gt; 1%&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ul</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"sidebar-nav motion-element"</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"sidebar-nav-toc sidebar-nav-active"</span> <span class="attr">data-target</span>=<span class="string">"post-toc-wrap"</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">            </span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123; __('sidebar.toc') &#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">        <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"sidebar-nav-overview"</span> <span class="attr">data-target</span>=<span class="string">"site-overview-wrap"</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">            </span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123; __('sidebar.overview') &#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">        <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"></span><span class="template-tag">&#123;% <span class="name"><span class="keyword">endif</span></span> %&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>分析源码可以得知，目录toc显示与否由<code>display_toc = is_post</code>以及<code>theme.toc.enable</code>或者<code>is_page</code>和<code>theme.toc.enable</code>控制<br>可以得知<code>display_toc = is_post</code>以及<code>is_page</code>是来区分当前页面是post上去的博客还是页面，而<code>theme.toc.enable</code>便为之前<code>_config.yml</code>文件中全局配置控制<br>如果修改<code>_config.yml</code>中<code>toc</code>下<code>enable</code>为false会导致所有文章页面都不自动生成目录<br>解决方法如下，将上方代码替换为如下代码：</p><figure class="highlight twig"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="xml"></span><span class="template-tag">&#123;% <span class="name"><span class="keyword">if</span></span> page.no_toc === undefined %&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">    </span><span class="template-tag">&#123;% <span class="name"><span class="keyword">set</span></span> display_toc = is_post and theme.toc.enable or is_page and theme.toc.enable %&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"></span><span class="template-tag">&#123;% <span class="name">else</span> %&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">    </span><span class="template-tag">&#123;% <span class="name"><span class="keyword">set</span></span> display_toc = is_post and theme.toc.enable and !page.no_toc or is_page and theme.toc.enable and !page.no_toc %&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"></span><span class="template-tag">&#123;% <span class="name"><span class="keyword">endif</span></span> %&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"></span><span class="template-tag">&#123;% <span class="name"><span class="keyword">if</span></span> display_toc and toc(page.content).length &gt; 1%&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ul</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"sidebar-nav motion-element"</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"sidebar-nav-toc sidebar-nav-active"</span> <span class="attr">data-target</span>=<span class="string">"post-toc-wrap"</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">            </span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123; __('sidebar.toc') &#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">        <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"sidebar-nav-overview"</span> <span class="attr">data-target</span>=<span class="string">"site-overview-wrap"</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">            </span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123; __('sidebar.overview') &#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">        <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"></span><span class="template-tag">&#123;% <span class="name"><span class="keyword">endif</span></span> %&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里添加了一个<code>page.no_toc</code>，它从你的页面或者post的博客的<code>font-matter</code>读取<code>no_toc</code>的配置信息，若<code>no_toc</code>未被定义，便自动生成目录。若定义了<code>no_toc</code>,便将<code>no_toc</code>加入到判断中，按如下设置即可禁用<code>toc</code>:</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">关于</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="number">2019</span><span class="bullet">-10</span><span class="bullet">-15</span> <span class="number">21</span><span class="string">:24:17</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">"about"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">no_toc:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="禁用自动toc生成编号"><a href="#禁用自动toc生成编号" class="headerlink" title="禁用自动toc生成编号"></a>禁用自动toc生成编号</h1><p>在上面提到在主题全局配置文件<code>_config.yml</code>中，自动编号是自动启动的<br>依旧在<code>主题根目录/layout/_macro/sidebar.swig</code>中，找到如下代码：</p><figure class="highlight django"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"post-toc"</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">    </span><span class="template-tag">&#123;% <span class="name"><span class="name">if</span></span> page.toc_number === undefined %&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">        </span><span class="template-tag">&#123;% <span class="name">set</span> toc = toc(page.content, &#123; "class": "nav", list_number: theme.toc.number &#125;) %&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">    </span><span class="template-tag">&#123;% <span class="name"><span class="name">else</span></span> %&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">        </span><span class="template-tag">&#123;% <span class="name">set</span> toc = toc(page.content, &#123; "class": "nav", list_number: page.toc_number &#125;) %&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">    </span><span class="template-tag">&#123;% <span class="name"><span class="name">endif</span></span> %&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">    </span><span class="template-tag">&#123;% <span class="name"><span class="name">if</span></span> toc.length &lt;= 1 %&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"post-toc-empty"</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123; __('post.toc_empty') &#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">    </span><span class="template-tag">&#123;% <span class="name"><span class="name">else</span></span> %&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"post-toc-content"</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123; toc &#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml">    </span><span class="template-tag">&#123;% <span class="name"><span class="name">endif</span></span> %&#125;</span><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>分析源码得知，若没有定义<code>toc_number</code>，他会根据主题<code>_config.yml</code>进行配置，即为<strong>true</strong>，定义了<code>toc_number</code>便从<code>font-matter</code>读取配置<br>所以我们只需在文章或者页面开头按如下设置即可：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">关于</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="number">2019</span><span class="bullet">-10</span><span class="bullet">-15</span> <span class="number">21</span><span class="string">:24:17</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">"about"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">toc_number:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><p>编辑于2019.10.16</p>]]></content>
    
